'''Little Duros''' was an district in [[Xakrea]] on [[Darkknell/Legends|Darkknell]] with a strong [[Duros/Legends|Duros]] population. [[Moranda Savich]] and [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Garm Bel Iblis]] spent some time in an open [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]] as part of a mission there around [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]].

